1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,520
Día uno

2
00:00:00,520 --> 00:00:01,360
buscando tesoros

3
00:00:01,360 --> 00:00:01,560
en bici

4
00:00:01,560 --> 00:00:02,600
por Valencia.

5
00:00:02,600 --> 00:00:03,640
A ver qué encontramos.

6
00:00:03,640 --> 00:00:04,080
Fijaos bien

7
00:00:04,080 --> 00:00:04,640
porque lo de hoy

8
00:00:04,640 --> 00:00:05,520
tiene tela.

9
00:00:05,520 --> 00:00:06,560
La ciudad está llena

10
00:00:06,560 --> 00:00:07,640
de cosas útiles

11
00:00:07,640 --> 00:00:08,400
escondidas

12
00:00:08,400 --> 00:00:09,000
a plena vista.

13
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:10,520
Pasas por delante

14
00:00:10,520 --> 00:00:11,480
y ni miras.

15
00:00:11,480 --> 00:00:11,800
Hoy iba

16
00:00:11,800 --> 00:00:13,080
por Exposición

17
00:00:13,080 --> 00:00:13,600
y ahí,

18
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:13,720
en medio

19
00:00:13,720 --> 00:00:15,000
de la acera...

20
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:16,000
una mesa negra.

21
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:16,520
Impecable.

22
00:00:16,520 --> 00:00:17,800
Tú pasas de largo

23
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:18,520
y no sabes

24
00:00:18,520 --> 00:00:19,440
lo que te pierdes.

25
00:00:19,440 --> 00:00:20,160
Y esto es algo

26
00:00:20,160 --> 00:00:20,880
que podemos hacer

27
00:00:20,880 --> 00:00:21,720
entre todos.

28
00:00:21,720 --> 00:00:22,440
Yo lo que hago

29
00:00:22,440 --> 00:00:23,320
es pararme,

30
00:00:23,320 --> 00:00:24,400
sacar la foto,

31
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:25,360
y dejarla en Givore.

32
00:00:25,360 --> 00:00:26,600
Treinta segundos.

33
00:00:26,600 --> 00:00:27,320
Y a partir de ahí

34
00:00:27,320 --> 00:00:28,000
la mesa ya no

35
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:28,760
es invisible.

36
00:00:28,760 --> 00:00:29,840
Cualquiera que pase

37
00:00:29,840 --> 00:00:30,160
por la app

38
00:00:30,160 --> 00:00:31,040
la va a ver.

39
00:00:31,040 --> 00:00:31,920
Y alguien va a decir

40
00:00:31,920 --> 00:00:32,720
eso es lo que

41
00:00:32,720 --> 00:00:33,840
andaba buscando.

42
00:00:33,840 --> 00:00:34,360
Hoy lo ha dicho

43
00:00:34,360 --> 00:00:35,120
alguien.

44
00:00:35,120 --> 00:00:35,760
Y se la ha llevado

45
00:00:35,760 --> 00:00:36,560
encantado.

46
00:00:36,560 --> 00:00:37,120
Si queréis ver

47
00:00:37,120 --> 00:00:37,600
más tesoros

48
00:00:37,600 --> 00:00:38,600
de Valencia...

49
00:00:38,600 --> 00:00:39,280
ya sabéis.

50
00:00:39,280 --> 00:00:40,240
Cada paseo

51
00:00:40,240 --> 00:00:41,400
encuentro algo nuevo.

